description:
Refactor this function to remove side effects and make it a pure function:

let total = 0;
function addToTotal(items: number[]): void {
  for (let i = 0; i < items.length; i++) {
    total += items[i];
  }
  console.log('Total:', total);
}

The refactored function should accept an array of numbers, return the sum, and not modify any external state or produce side effects.
